            <title>[SEC-2530] BasicAuthenticationFilter does not respect charset encoding</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SEC-2530</link>
                <project id="10040" key="SEC">Spring Security</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;BasicAuthenticationFilter has hard coded char set UTF-8.&lt;br/&gt;
But according to RFC2616, RFC2617 it should be iso-8859-1 or detected with mime format which does not happen too.&lt;/p&gt;

